{"tid":94132,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"今日係我生日 但係我一啲都唔開心","createTime":"2017-01-25T03:45:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-25T06:19:57.000Z","uid":11215,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f24acc6b41f67dc040de4fcc24fa16da25a79278","tid":94132,"uid":11215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T03:45:21.000Z","msg":"呢嗰係我成世人第一個開嘅post<br />\n今日係我生日 但係我一啲都無開心嘅感覺<br />\n讀書讀到final year但係我對前路仲係一啲頭緒都無<br />\n細個就想入大學 而家大學畢業我發覺自己乜嘢目標都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n女朋友我有但係佢對我感覺越來越淡 今日我生日我地連見都應該無得見 屋企人全部都唔係翻工就出咗去<br />\n<br />\n我覺得人生好孤獨 好無目標同意義<br />\n有無人可以開解下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69bd2baa226ebf1002456e9709b161a2ddf0aec6","tid":94132,"uid":71671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T03:58:15.000Z","msg":"男人老狗仲講生日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ea000dd5e16ab3a6b99b319d9d9857d058d9a0b","tid":94132,"uid":27793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T04:03:22.000Z","msg":"同你年紀差唔多<br />\n你讀廢科咩？咁sad既你講到個前景<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35c68a2055101d46badd4e32c24c929383909be2","tid":94132,"uid":39338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T04:03:37.000Z","msg":"&quot;女朋友我有......&quot;<br />\n<br />\n此post已完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96021dd295e3722a256807e22cd8fdb7cc763edf","tid":94132,"uid":27793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T04:03:54.000Z","msg":"btw 生日快樂啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n約朋友吖嘛<br />\n你要搵多啲兄弟<br />\n唔好忽略佢地"},{"pid":"205e065cbc49f07a9c20819ab88d146cb8c6c71b","tid":94132,"uid":3162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T04:05:46